channel.title: Fedexer's Global Object Tut Error
channel.description:
I am helping a friend code his server for him, and I added some bank booths in Fally Garden using Fedexer's Global Object Tutorial, but he keeps getting this error: [code]client.java:725: cannot find symbol symbol : method makeGlobalObject(int,int,int,int,int) location: class client makeGlobalObject(2998, 3373, 2213, -1, 10);//bank booth ^[/code] It does this for all 5 of the booths I added. Anyone know the solution?
P.S. I've tried changing "makeGlobalObject" to "MakeGlobalObject", "AddGlobalObject", and "addGlobalObject" and he still got the same errors.
